        {
            "title": "利率不降就炒貝森特魷魚 川普對財長的玩笑暗諷鮑威爾",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:川普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/川普\">川普</a>暗示，如果<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>不能幫助推動利率下降，他將解雇這位財政部長。這一表態側面反映出川普對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>不願快速降息的不滿。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「斯科特唯一搞砸的就是聯儲會，」川普周三在華盛頓舉行的美沙投資論壇上說，「利率太高了，斯科特，如果你不盡快解決，我就炒你魷魚，怎麼樣？」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dpndL7arGcPwCmJUL.rStw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1a52d61cfee62feba551ef9785788f7d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著選民要求降低生活成本的呼聲漸高，白宮面臨越來越大的政治壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普重申，他「很想解雇」聯儲會主席傑羅姆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>，因為其「嚴重無能」。他重申，鮑威爾應該因主導聯儲會總部昂貴的翻修工程而被起訴。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d12f71f0-7d40-3a2f-9890-92f562f6df81-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普證實，是財政部長貝森特勸阻他不要強行將鮑威爾撤職。貝森特曾對他說：「先生，請別炒他魷魚，他只剩三個月任期了」。川普告訴在場觀眾，貝森特代表著「理性的聲音」，「你們有他真是幸運，我可以告訴你們，他干得很好。」 聯儲會觀察人士此前警告稱，若鮑威爾被強行解職，將引發市場震盪，並削弱外界對央行獨立性的信心。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在提到商務部長霍華德·盧特尼克時笑稱，「我覺得霍華德可能更贊成炒掉鮑威爾，我想他會說，‘趕緊把那家伙弄出去吧。’」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：會議紀要凸顯聯儲會分歧 「許多」官員不贊成12月進一步降息</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為財政部長，貝森特並不直接掌控利率。聯儲會聯邦公開市場委員會(FOMC)才是決定基準政策利率的機構。該委員會今年已兩次投票將利率下調25個基點，但川普一直要求以更激進的速度降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會拒絕就川普言論置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Quips He’ll Fire Bessent If Interest Rates Are Not Lowered</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Christopher Condon.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新川普更多評論)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
